  "texts": [
    "Market resources such as (price, advertisement, distribution) and market knowledge capabilities (Morgan 2012; Hou and Chien 2010) also play a significant role in business performance.",
    "• Investment and Market relationship: Investment is directly related to the market.",
    "Market increasing, such as a stock market, often promotes product sales etc., increased investment.",
    "Investors tend to invest in stocks showing clear growth in the company's stocks and shares (Vui et al. 2013; Barro 1990).",
    "Based on this analysis, we can observe that investments shift to follow the market."
  ]
}